ran slickly produced TV ads like this.

258
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:23,760
As a mobile law enforcement arm
of the Department of Homeland Security,

259
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:25,960
it is the job of the Border Patrol

260
00:14:26,040 --> 00:14:28,760
to prevent terrorists
and terrorist weapons

261
00:14:28,880 --> 00:14:32,960
and all those who seek to do us harm
from entering the United States.

262
00:14:43,160 --> 00:14:46,720
The Border Patrol.
We protect America.

263
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,480
Are you up to the challenge ?

264
00:14:48,920 --> 00:14:52,160
You have to admit, they make that job
look very exciting.

265
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:53,440
Although, in fairness,

266
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:56,480
anything said in that tone of voice
would be exciting.

267
00:14:56,560 --> 00:14:58,800
"Here is my kitten.
I named him Bootsie."

268
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:00,560
"Don't wee on the rug, Bootsie !"

269
00:15:00,640 --> 00:15:03,360
"I'm not sure he likes me
