270
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:07,400
But the truth of their job is

271
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:11,440
that most agents work alone
patrolling vast swaths of desert.

272
00:15:11,520 --> 00:15:13,480
And while some days feature
bursts of action,

273
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:15,800
others can involve
absolutely nothing,

274
00:15:15,920 --> 00:15:18,040
which can be challenging
in and of itself.

275
00:15:18,280 --> 00:15:21,000
One of the larger problems is boredom.

276
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:23,400
It doesn't mean
that it's never dangerous.

277
00:15:23,520 --> 00:15:27,160
There are bandits out there;
there are drug organizations out there.

278
00:15:27,640 --> 00:15:31,000
What they're not really getting
is preparation

279
00:15:31,160 --> 00:15:38,120
for the boring non-risky reality
of almost all of their career.

280
00:15:38,960 --> 00:15:44,000
Exactly. Boredom is a significant part
of life as a Border Patrol agent.

281
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:45,680
And they should probably train for it.

282
00:15:45,760 --> 00:15:47,960
For every hour they spend
in target practice,

283
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:51,920
