and systematically driving carnivores
whales insane.

344
00:18:49,360 --> 00:18:51,160
That's the whole job there.

345
00:18:51,280 --> 00:18:54,080
Take them away.
You're left with nothing else.

346
00:18:54,840 --> 00:18:56,640
And consequently as the ranks grew,

347
00:18:56,720 --> 00:18:59,240
corruption and excessive force
skyrocketed.

348
00:18:59,360 --> 00:19:02,680
Misconduct became such a problem
that, at one point,

349
